title: Australia's Next Top Model - S10E01
description:
Australia's Next Top Model - S10E01

It's the tenth series of Australia's Next Top Model and the competition is the most fierce it's ever been. This year, Jennifer Hawkins is joined by new judge Megan Gale and series veteran Alex Perry on the judging panel, and Jordan and Zac Stenmark combine forces with Cheyenne Tozzi as model mentors. The top thirteen are thrown in the deep end on day one with an Alex Perry runway challenge in front of 400 people. They then have to impress in the photo shoot, which is a face-off with the winner of series 7, Montana Cox. The episode culminates in an emotion-charged elimination, as one girl's story brings Megan to tears.
